Thats a new hunter difficulty, hunters can't very good spawn killing zombies. They can't see into the spawn of zombies, there is a black wall they can't walk into it, but zombies can walk out. Zombie comes of all sides!, teamplay is required to survive, a door in the middle opens in 100seconds to get a help.

***********************************************************************

Counter-Terrorist (Hunters) = 16 Spawnpoints
Terrorist (Zombies) = 16 Spawnpoints
